---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="La Transnacionalización - Marco Sintético">
  <main class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold text-4xl text-on-surface mb-3">
        La Transnacionalización
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Mapeo técnico de flujos de innovación, planificación y mercados dentro
        de la arquitectura global corporativa.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative w-full aspect-[16/10] bg-surface-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-md border border-outline-variant/30"
    >
      <svg
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 1000 625"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
      >
        <defs>
          <marker
            id="arrowhead-primary"
            markerHeight="7"
            markerWidth="10"
            orient="auto"
            refX="9"
            refY="3.5"
          >
            <polygon fill="#0061a4" points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7"></polygon>
          </marker>
          <marker
            id="arrowhead-primary-reverse"
            markerHeight="7"
            markerWidth="10"
            orient="auto"
            refX="1"
            refY="3.5"
          >
            <polygon fill="#0061a4" points="10 0, 0 3.5, 10 7"></polygon>
          </marker>
          <marker
            id="arrowhead-secondary"
            markerHeight="7"
            markerWidth="10"
            orient="auto"
            refX="9"
            refY="3.5"
          >
            <polygon fill="#565f71" points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7"></polygon>
          </marker>
          <marker
            id="arrowhead-secondary-reverse"
            markerHeight="7"
            markerWidth="10"
            orient="auto"
            refX="1"
            refY="3.5"
          >
            <polygon fill="#565f71" points="10 0, 0 3.5, 10 7"></polygon>
          </marker>
        </defs>

        <style>
          svg text {
            font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 500;
            fill: #43474e;
          }
        </style>

        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow1" startOffset="50%">
            <tspan dy="-20">Transferencia de</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">tecnología innovada</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          id="flow1"
          d="M 240 213 C 300 160, 350 140, 410 130"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#0061a4"
          stroke-width="2"
          marker-start="url(#arrowhead-primary-reverse)"
        >
        </path>

        <path
          id="flow2"
          d="M 590 130 C 650 140, 700 160, 760 213"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#0061a4"
          stroke-width="2"
          marker-start="url(#arrowhead-primary-reverse)"></path>

        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow2" startOffset="50%">
            <tspan dy="-20">Apropiación de</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">innovación</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          id="flow3"
          d="M 595 515 C 660 500, 760 480, 790 400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#0061a4"
          stroke-width="2"
          marker-start="url(#arrowhead-primary-reverse)"></path>

        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow3" startOffset="60%">
            <tspan dy="18">Transferencia de la</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">planificación económica</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          id="flow4"
          d="M 190 390 C 210 470, 330 495, 410 515"
          fill="none"
          stroke="#0061a4"
          stroke-width="2"
          marker-end="url(#arrowhead-primary)"
        >
        </path>
        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow4" startOffset="60%">
            <tspan dy="20">Transferencia de la</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">planificación política</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          d="M 280 240 C 300 235, 380 200, 420 165"
          fill="none"
          id="flow5"
          marker-end="url(#arrowhead-secondary)"
          stroke="#565f71"
          stroke-width="2"></path>
        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow5" startOffset="40%">
            <tspan dy="-20">Apropiación de</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">mercados</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          d="M 550 165 C 600 200, 710 235, 720 240"
          fill="none"
          id="flow6"
          marker-end="url(#arrowhead-secondary)"
          stroke="#565f71"
          stroke-width="2"></path>
        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow6" startOffset="45%">
            <tspan dy="-20">Transferencia de</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">tecnologia obsoleta</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          d="M 580 460 Q 652 375 725 365"
          fill="none"
          id="flow7"
          marker-start="url(#arrowhead-secondary-reverse)"
          stroke="#565f71"
          stroke-width="2"></path>
        <text dy="15">
          <textPath startOffset="50%" text-anchor="middle" xlink:href="#flow7">
            <tspan dy="15">Apropiación</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">administrativa</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>

        <path
          d="M 280 380 C 280 375, 380 395, 450 460"
          fill="none"
          id="flow8"
          marker-end="url(#arrowhead-secondary)"
          stroke="#565f71"
          stroke-width="2"></path>
        <text text-anchor="middle">
          <textPath href="#flow8" startOffset="40%">
            <tspan dy="18">Apropiación de</tspan>
            <tspan x="0" dy="12">tecnología</tspan>
          </textPath>
        </text>
      </svg>

      <div
        class="absolute left-[10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col items-center"
      >
        <div
          class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/20"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/transnacionalizacion/trasnacionalizacion.png"
            alt="Transnacional"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-2"
        >
          Transnacional
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute left-1/2 top-[10%] -translate-x-1/2 w-48 bg-surface-container-highest p-4 rounded-2xl text-center border border-outline-variant/20"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2 text-3xl"
          >factory</span
        >
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary">
          Filial de Producción
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
        >
          Núcleo Operativo
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute right-[10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col items-center"
      >
        <div
          class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/20"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/transnacionalizacion/multinacional.png"
            alt="Multinacional"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-2"
        >
          Multinacional
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute left-1/2 bottom-[10%] -translate-x-1/2 w-48 bg-surface-container-highest p-4 rounded-2xl text-center border border-outline-variant/20"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-2 text-3xl"
          >conveyor_belt</span
        >
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary">Filial de Relevo</h3>
        <p
          class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
        >
          Soporte Estratégico
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div
        class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
          <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary">
            Flujos de Transferencia
          </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Representa el movimiento circular de recursos, normativas y activos
          tecnológicos desde la matriz hacia los nodos operativos y
          estratégicos.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-secondary"></span>
          <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-secondary">
            Flujos de Apropiación
          </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Indica la captura de valor, datos de mercado y retornos estratégicos
          que circulan internamente para fortalecer la red global.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary">info</span>
          <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-tertiary">
            Protocolos de Red
          </h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          La visualización clockwise (sentido horario) unifica la lógica
          operativa y política bajo un modelo de equilibrio cívico y flujo
          continuo.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
